      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against analytical solutions or established benchmark problems relevant to rotating machinery flows.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against Taylor-Couette flow analytical solution and lid-driven cavity benchmark. Residuals converge below 1e-5 for all transport equations."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
