      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric defined; CFD predictions within acceptable tolerance of experimental hemolysis measurements.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared between CFD predictions and experimental measurements across all 5 operating points. Mean absolute error of 8.4% within the 15% acceptance tolerance defined for MRL 2."
    },
    {
