      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s), density (1060 kg/m³), and hemolysis model constants documented with literature sources. Sensitivity to ±10% input variation assessed informally; RH index variation below 5%. Formal uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
    },
