    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4 at MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH index predictions within 15% tolerance of experimental data across all evaluated operating points. Decision: model is fit for purpose for the stated COU.",
